  "detailed_description": "Creepy Forest, a scary plot puzzle game, is full of strange things waiting for you to discover the truth on the mysterious mountain.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193900/extras/8b0e18992934a1234ae238104284f1d5.avif?t=1673679301\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br>You will manipulate the protagonist and uncover the long-standing horror story on the mountain;<br>The whole plot is mainly decrypted, the puzzle design is moderately difficult, and it is closely combined with the plot, bringing an immersive experience.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193900/extras/425ec50368b8fb0405209de983b5ac0c.avif?t=1673679301\" width=600 height=336 /></span>",
